title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Oct 17 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Oct 17 2022
description:
Nike co-founder Phil Knight backs Amazin' Drazan in Oregon. Mark Ronchetti joins C&B to tell us why he will be the next New Mexico governor. Clay rejoices, gets emotional as the Vols hold back the Crimson Tide for a big win.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
